      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GALWAY CHARM (1) went down narrowly last time, finishing a nose second behind Witchetty Grub in 16.79 and recording a new PB this course and distance. Smart run latest and looks a key chance here. KICKER ZOOM (3) hit the ground running and never headed to claim a maiden victory two back then finished a 13 length eighth last start at Q Lakeside over 390m (22.94). Well placed here and should do much better. EVEN STEVENS (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.38 beating Sweet Michelle. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. PROFESSOR SHOGUN (8) is worth a look despite no experience at this circuit.",
